    // dp[i][mask] represents the maximum value achievable with the first i elements and a certain mask
    // mask is a 3-bit number representing which elements are in A, B, C
    // 000: all elements are in A
    // 001: all elements are in B
    // 010: all elements are in C
    // 011: some elements are in A, some in B, some in C
